Key Match Events: Christian Braun posterized Rudy Gobert with a two-handed slam, leading to double technical fouls on both players.
The Denver Nuggets lost to the Minnesota Timberwolves with a final score of 119-116.
Pre-Game Insights: Denver entered the game hoping for a win over their conference rivals in the rematch after losing to Minnesota in seven games during last season's Western Conference Semifinals.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Christian Braun's dunk has been going viral on social media, with several major sports outlets posting the highlight play.
Braun's teammates immediately ran to defend him after Gobert made contact with the 23-year-old guard.
